  <evidenceContent rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">You can choose to have your computer warn you each time a cookie is being sent or you can choose to turn off all cookies You do this through your browser e g Microsoft Internet Explorer Mozilla Firefox Google Chrome or Apple Safari settings Each browser is a little different so look at your browser Help menu to learn the correct way to modify your cookies If you turn cookies off you won t have access to many features that make your Site experience more efficient and some of our services will not function properly</evidenceContent>
